<h3>View your Cloud Storage buckets in the Cloud console</h3>
<ul>
<li>Return to the Cloud console and from the <strong>Navigation menu</strong> go to <strong>Cloud Storage &gt; Buckets</strong> to ensure that your Cloud Storage buckets were created.</li>
</ul>
<p>Remain in the Cloud console for the following step. Keep the APIs Explorer tab open.</p>
<h2 id="step6">Task 3. Upload files to your Cloud Storage bucket</h2>
<p>Upload some files to your Cloud Storage bucket so you can get hands-on practice with methods housed in the APIs explorer.</p>
<ol>
<li>Save the following image to your computer and name it <strong>demo-image1.png</strong>:</li>
</ol>
<p><button class="js-img-container" aria-haspopup="true"><img alt="Dog" src="./demo-image2_files/E4+Sx10I0HBeOFPB15BFPzf9__OK+tf7S0Mbn6aQ8fw="></button></p>
<ol start="2">
<li>Now save this public domain image of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ada_Lovelace" target="_blank">Ada Lovelace</a> to your computer and name it <strong>demo-image2.png</strong>:</li>
</ol>
<p><button class="js-img-container" aria-haspopup="true"><img alt="Ada Lovelace" src="./demo-image2_files/Hr8ohUSBSeAiMUJe1J998ydGcTu_rF4BUjZ2J+biKps="></button></p>
<ol start="3">
<li>
<p>In the Cloud Storage browser select the first bucket from the list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click <strong>Upload</strong> &gt; <strong>Upload files</strong> and select <strong>demo-image1.png</strong> and <strong>demo-image2.png</strong> from your computer.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p>Your bucket should now have both image files added to it and should resemble the following:</p>
<p><button class="js-img-container" aria-haspopup="true"><img alt="demo-image1.png and demo-image2.png listed on the Objects tabbed page of qwiklabs-bucket01" src="./demo-image2_files/KUv+vmFEU+TG6k64oqwh2vqjzccr3Wetjge0rOrZUr4="></button></p>
<p>Click <em>Check my progress</em> to verify the objective.
<ql-activity-tracking step="3" labinstanceid="143483512"><template shadowrootmode="open"><!---->
      <ql-assessment aria-label=""><template shadowrootmode="open"><!---->
      <div class="assessment-left">
        <ql-assessment-status><template shadowrootmode="open"><!---->
      <div class="status" role="progressbar" aria-live="assertive" status="initialized" tooltip="" aria-hidden="true" aria-valuenow="0" aria-label=""><!--?lit$712519209$--></div>
    </template>
        </ql-assessment-status>
      </div>

