<p><button class="js-img-container" aria-haspopup="true"><img alt="204 displayed on a green ribbon" src="./demo-image2_files/nRkqUtiQhhbyhJr7SILoziHp5HZOH39Vlr+8ES9Winc="></button></p>
<p>You have successfully deleted a bucket using the  <code>buckets.delete</code> method.</p>
<h3>View your updated bucket in the Cloud console</h3>
